➜一秒变蛇精！靠脸吃饭的大明星们，求求你们卸载掉美图软件吧！
http://www.sohu.com/a/324988073_407929	18933
<p class="ql-align-justify">想在这个夏天瘦十斤脸变小最快的方法是什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">开滤镜！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">​</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">前几天网红直播间的郭富城就享受了这待遇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">郭富城一开始撅着嘴，有些拘谨。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/cfdc2c88fd444082ae135d5edd5e7abe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">看到镜头下的自己一下就乐了，这恐怕是我的大眼瘦脸的巅峰~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/9195eaa392bd4a888e64cc26ce29f140.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">眼睛是大，但是就少了郭天王那份刚毅的英气和男人味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/3c148af4fceb479193f5356d87cf5e2a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/45275e34631041c9a9a484df1b0e74ac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">作为老百姓自嗨的第一法宝，美颜滤镜已经普及到用原相机拍照的人统统被喷直男的程度了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">普通人开滤镜能变好看，但对明星来说，那可是心灵暴击式的灾难啊！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">佘诗曼第一次看到网红滤镜里的自己时，露出了尴尬而不失礼貌的微笑。<img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/042ef87fb1d84ef7842c275ccea1b51c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然后挂着端正的微笑着离开了镜头，事后她坦言，其实是被吓到了…</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/b3c13ea2e4f74499933196e7f99c59f5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">简单自然，笑容甜甜，这才是阿佘的正确打开方式嘛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/c1fe71fc77b146889cb41e5cd49a269a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">和佘诗曼在《延禧攻略》演对手戏的吴谨言也跳不过滤镜的魔爪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">ok，于妈我知道了，你脸小，可是你旁边这个女人是谁？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/7bdca8083a4c4a2385b0e6e3cbad81b5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我以为吴谨言是长这样的……</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/8ab05bb5c6024f97a5aaf0e74f59697c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">祸害了吴谨言还不够，于妈整个剧组都不放过。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/4cf05e2787c64d87a508dee4c5e4bd6b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">惊不惊喜！意不意外！爱不爱！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在合照里，秦岚看起来一下没有了辨识度，还有那个尖下巴的男人，你说你叫聂远？信不信我打你？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/27d5b3961da343afb63ec57749a9f44c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">明星们虽然见多识广，但显然不清楚网红滤镜到底有多强大。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">看看赵薇这一脸惊讶又按捺不住好笑的样子。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/b455f42920614f2f9cd98ff6804836ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">佟大为则是瞪大了他blingbling的好奇小眼睛：这个男人和我好像！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/954b928b7d124bcabe18c182be6dc291.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是有那么一点像……</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/a97b53e4992f44cd84e1f960e9353287.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">王源就皱着眉一言难尽，这个长脸怪是谁？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/fc70ab12a147428aa9963cd0575f22fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">相比之下，使用同款hello Kitty滤镜的郭京飞就淡定多了，只是娴静中透露一丝看不懂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/8e76718cf2174c5280098043785df48c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">？？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/3b60b843f75e441995c16782fe95ef87.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">baby更是见怪不怪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">说起来，angelababy本来就是小脸大眼的代表，但是在美颜滤镜下真的有些恐怖。这大眼瞪着，下巴尖着真的是人类吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/97a5c0b475154558a7aed14b0a3de81a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">看张美照压压惊……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/e361a6021d444b62acef0ed4ba00af61.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">痞帅风格的张一山加了萌系滤镜之后看起来乖多了，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/5f567824a9ce4dfe803e7f5cbf7cdbec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但是没有小流氓气质的张一山根本就不是好刘星！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/5d07df5f16104e3a9257c7b775e06ccc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">就好比如大眼卖萌的沈腾失去了喜剧演员的灵魂！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/dcf3036b636f44e7aa81dc994000dd14.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这才是在我笑点上生根发芽的男人！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/49626bd3148743aa9f1a9616d58c4b21.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">雷佳音在滤镜下失去了他赖以生存的大头，变成了高贵精致的公子哥，只是眉宇之间暗藏着一份忧郁和茫然。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/8978ca86d7aa487f84b97a4365781037.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">或许他是在怀念那个恣意潇洒的糙汉？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/663ab66786fa442486676b8a2215a38d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">当然，滤镜这么多，只要套餐选的对，明星颜值也可以加成，至少不那么违和。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/7e38eb21a59a435981bd76245eb922e5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但我觉得还是原图更顺眼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190705/8d3a91688cf2424dab439feed0fada0e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">毕竟网红滤镜是给我们这些平凡人遮瑕的，大眼小脸高鼻梁，只要往大众审美的方向靠拢就能让普通人变好看。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但是明星之所以成为明星，是因为他们本身长相过关。网红滤镜一味地大眼小脸白皮，只能磨灭明星本身特有的韵味和识别度。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大明星们还是好好去荧幕上呆着吧~</p>